1964;;The Scarlet Blade;;British;;John Gilling;;Jack Hedley, Oliver Reed, Lionel Jeffries;;action;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Scarlet_Blade;;When King Charles I is captured by Roundhead forces led by the tyrant Colonel Judd and his right-hand man Captain Sylvester. It is up to a band of locals loyal to the King to try to rescue him. They are helped by Judd's daughter Claire who secretly helps them in defiance of her father.